::Shadow Wing::

She ran as fast as she could.  But with the dagger wound in her leg, 
she couldn't run fast enough. Her side hurt from Killers first slash 
at her and now her hand was gone. She hoped that she could make it to 
the Ark and prayed to the Matrix that her wing would heal faster so 
she could fly out of there.  Lunarpine was right in that I'd never 
make it in a real fight, she told herself and kept running.  She was 
getting tired and the pain was dragging her down.
